  "text": "A 3D-clinostat was used to simulate reduced gravity for gravity sensitive cell [CITATION_1] . The 3D-clinostat was designed to fit the incubator. The size of the center plates was 160 mm by 106 mm. To operate the 3D-clinostat, two motors were used. The instrument could rotate linearly whose direction is clockwise (CW) and counter clockwise (CCW) and rotate at 2 rpm.",
